        crm:P2_has_type               <urn:uuid:68379a31-4d53-4590-b941-01998e68d376> ;
        crm:P3_has_note               "IoT sensors embedded in the Smart Display Case collect time-stamped readings for temperature, relative humidity, illuminance, vibration/shock events, and access events (opening/closing status). Data are transmitted to the ARTEMIS platform via MQTT and RESTful APIs at intervals between 60 seconds and one reading per hour. An edge processing unit (ESP32 or Raspberry Pi) buffers data locally in case of connectivity loss. The operation runs continuously throughout the pilot period." ;
